'''提高石油采收率技术'''（Enhanced Oil Recovery，简称'''EOR'''）是指向油藏中注入驱油剂或调剖剂，改善油藏及油藏流体的[[物理|物理]][[化学|化学]]特性、提高宏观波及效率和微观驱油效率的采油方法，统称为提高石油采收率技术，或称“强化采油技术”。提高原油采收率也被称为三级采油（与一级采油和二级采油相反）。 据美国能源部称，EOR有三种主要技术：热回收，气体注入和化学品注入<ref name="DOE Fossil">{{cite web|title=Enhanced Oil Recovery|url=http://energy.gov/fe/science-innovation/oil-gas-research/enhanced-oil-recovery|website=www.doe.gov|publisher=U.S. Department of Energy|access-date=2018-06-19|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602140655/https://www.energy.gov/fe/science-innovation/oil-gas-research/enhanced-oil-recovery|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有时四级采收（quaternary recovery）术语被用于指更先进的，推测性的EOR技术<ref name="Hobson">{{cite book|last=Hobson |first=George Douglas |author2=Eric Neshan Tiratsoo|title=Introduction to petroleum geology|url=https://archive.org/details/introductiontope0000hobs |publisher=Scientific Press|year=1975|isbn=9780901360076}}</ref><ref name="Walsh">{{cite book|last=Walsh|first=Mark |author2=Larry W. Lake|title=A generalized approach to primary hydrocarbon recovery|publisher=Elsevier|year=2003}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development|title=21st century technologies|publisher=OECD Publishing|series=1998|pages=39|isbn=9789264160521}}</ref><ref name="Smith">{{cite book|last=Smith|first=Charles|title=Mechanics of secondary oil recovery|url=https://archive.org/details/mechanicsofsecon0000unse|publisher=Reinhold Pub. Corp|year=1966}}</ref>。使用EOR，可以提取30％至60％或更多的油藏里原本的石油，而使用一级的和二级的采收率为20％至40％<ref>Electric Power Research Institute, Palo Alto, CA (1999). [http://www.energy.ca.gov/process/pubs/electrotech_opps_tr113836.pdf "Enhanced Oil Recovery Scoping Study."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.energy.ca.gov/process/pubs/electrotech_opps_tr113836.pdf |date=20170120114926 }} Final Report, No. TR-113836.</ref><ref>Clean Air Task Force (2009). [http://www.coaltransition.org/pages/_enhanced_oil_recovery__eor__/154.php "About EOR"]  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313143356/http://www.coaltransition.org/pages/_enhanced_oil_recovery__eor__/154.php |date=March 13, 2012 }}</ref>。

==技术分类==
EOR有三种主要技术：注气，热注入和化学注入。 在美国，采用天然气，氮气或二氧化碳（CO2）等气体的天然气注入量占EOR产量的近60％[1]。 热喷射涉及热量的产生，在美国占EOR产量的40％，其中大部分发生在加利福尼亚州<ref name="DOE Fossil"/>。 化学品注入可能涉及使用称为聚合物的长链分子来提高注水的有效性，它占<ref name="DOE Fossil"/>美国EOR产量的大约1％<ref name="DOE Fossil"/>。 2013年，美国从俄罗斯引进了被称为等离子脉冲（Plasma-Pulse）的技术。 这种技术可以使现有油井产量再提高50％<ref name="Press Release">{{cite web|url=http://www.prweb.com/releases/enhanced_oil_recovery/oil_services/prweb10316946.htm|title=Novas Energy USA Open Offices in Houston, Texas to Introduce its Proprietary Enhanced Oil Recovery Technology in the United States|publisher=|access-date=2018-06-19|archive-date=2017-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226120427/http://www.prweb.com/releases/enhanced_oil_recovery/oil_services/prweb10316946.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

